aafokovol.name: aafokovol
aafokovol.description: A post-apocalyptic language of two scripts and a culture based on the denial of scientific progress

ciscun.name: ciscun
ciscun.description: Ya need a turtle? Ya got a turtle

hantera.name: hantera
hantera.description: a conpidgin that texas made with some friends

illyrian.name: illyrian
illyrian.description: The better of the texas conlangs. Spoken in an alternate-universe Dalmatian region.

olamolh.name: olamolh
olamolh.description: A language with a Spanish-inspired orthography and complex grammar that makes heavy use of non-concatenative morphology including benfeactive suffixes for verbs and possessive suffixes for nouns spoken traditionally buy a group of hunter-gatherer tribes but has now expanded to an entire country which sits between the United States and Mexico.

osrhean.name: osrhean
osrhean.description: A Romance conlang, heavily inspired by Portuguese.

rasna.name: rasna
rasna.description: Rasna (aka. Classic Atlantean) is spoken by the people of Atlantis. It has strong lexical connections with Etruscan and some ancient Indo-European languages.

tsevhu.name: tsevhu
tsevhu.description: Tsevhu [tsɛˈβu] n. constructed art-language made by koallary centered around the basis of a free-order volition controlled grammar system and a hidden non-linear writing system created using koi fish and ripples.
